2023-10-12  Reini Urban  <rurban@cpan.org>

	encode: disable downconvert_relative_handle
	Of course r2000 can read relative handles just fine.
	They are mandatory for prev,next_entity links.
	Just first,last_ links and similar 4 links were always absolute.
	Just VX_TABLE_RECORD.ownerhandle is relative.

	But this must be defined in the caller, if obj or NULL.

