	type before size

	2ndheader: fix unknown_rc4 reset hack
	no dat->byte -= 2, check unknown_10 for subsequent length 2 or 4
	just for json stay with length 4 for now, as in_json _INL cannot decide on 2/4 yet.

	decode: better 2ndheader logging
	spezialize the section and handlers repeats

2023-08-04  Reini Urban  <rurban@cpan.org>

	decode: enhance APPINFO.max_decomp_size
	as seen in GH #797

2023-08-04  Michal Josef Špaček  <michal.josef.spacek@gmail.com>

	Improve logging of addresses

2023-08-03  Michal Josef Špaček  <michal.josef.spacek@gmail.com>

	Improve logging output for unknown_rc4 in second header
	Main intent is removing of [i], not intuitive

	Before:
	unknown_rc4[i]: 0x78 [RC 0]
	unknown_rc4[i]: 0x1 [RC 0]
	unknown_rc4[i]: 0x5 [RC 0]
	unknown_rc4[i]: 0x0 [RC 0]

	After:
	unknown_rc4[0]: 0x78 [RC 0]
	unknown_rc4[1]: 0x1 [RC 0]
	unknown_rc4[2]: 0x5 [RC 0]
	unknown_rc4[3]: 0x0 [RC 0]

2023-08-03  Michal Josef Špaček  <michal.josef.spacek@gmail.com>

	Improve logging output for second header null_b[]
	Improve logging output

	Main intent is removing of [i], not intuitive

	Before:
	null_b[i]: 0 [B 0]
	null_b[i]: 0 [B 0]
	null_b[i]: 0 [B 0]
	null_b[i]: 0 [B 0]

	After:
	null_b[0]: 0 [B 0]
	null_b[1]: 0 [B 0]
	null_b[2]: 0 [B 0]
	null_b[3]: 0 [B 0]

2023-08-03  Michal Josef Špaček  <michal.josef.spacek@gmail.com>

