	Fix dxf in FIELD_VECTOR_INL logging

2023-08-03  Michal Josef Špaček  <michal.josef.spacek@gmail.com>

	Improve logging output for zero_5 header variable
	Main intent is removing of [i], not intuitive

	Before:
	zero_5[i]: 0x0 [RC 0]
	zero_5[i]: 0x0 [RC 0]
	zero_5[i]: 0x0 [RC 0]
	zero_5[i]: 0x0 [RC 0]
	zero_5[i]: 0x0 [RC 0]

	After:
	zero_5[0]: 0x0 [RC]
	zero_5[1]: 0x0 [RC]
	zero_5[2]: 0x0 [RC]
	zero_5[3]: 0x0 [RC]
	zero_5[4]: 0x0 [RC]

