	alive.test: add more preR13 tests
	example_r13 and r1.4/entities are stable.
	r11/entities r10/entities r2.x/entities fail rw.

	FIXME: chibicc fails at bit_read_4BITS_tests

	-Winline eed_need_size
	gcc4 says: eed_need_size.isra.3: call is unlikely and code size would grow

