	now that I can cross-compile it on linux via clang-cl (cmake and ninja),
	and added a CI for VS2019 on Windows.
	via ucrt, so only newer Visual Studio's.
	See previous commits.

	Fix some wrong types along the way, clang-cl x86_64 finds much more
	deviating integer sizes.

