	r11: add weird LINE.unknown_r11 GH #586
	On some lines only, not backed up by some flag or opts.
	The DXF misses those 2 numbers.
	E.g.
	start: (20.000000, 51.000000) [2RD 10]
	end: (20.000000, -51.000000) [2RD 11]
	unknown_r11: (-3.626858, 10.000000) [2RD 0]

