2022-07-29  Reini Urban  <rurban@cpan.org>

	fixup Fixes Heap-buffer-overflow in dwg_decode_MINSERT_private
	invalid bit_advance_position fix.
	we need to advance it, even when out-of-bounds

	fixup decode_r2007 off-by-one
	commit fe03c5a89cbd441b6840335bd484cf08bc65c7c4 only set the size for one case,
	but we had three. Fix the real problem, the dest overflow check.

	unit-testing: enable preR13 DWGs

