2022-04-14  Reini Urban  <rurban@cpan.org>

	<R13: add dwg_decode_preR13_header_variables
	the spec fields return on error. so wrap it.
	improve decoding the tables.

	spec: fix clang -Wtautological-constant-out-of-range-compare
	RCu can be max 255, then it wraps around

