	spec: add 25 UNKNOWN SECTION, improve auxheader.spec
	document the beta dwg_version fields

	work on ACAC103-4 support
	There's only a single example dwg though, and this might be
	from a beta revision.

	simplify dwg versions
	use a single array of releases, headers, versions.
	and add all the possible DWG versions (also the not yet seen,
	and the versions which did not change the DWG).

