	llvmfuzz: close the null file-handle
	running out of it

	Fix dwg2dxf uppercase extension problem
	GH #311, esp on Windows

	indxf: detect dxf_read_* premature DXF end
	A DXF line must end with \n.
	detected via llvmfuzz

