2020-11-12  Reini Urban  <rurban@cpan.org>

	spec: add DEBUGGING BLOCKREPRESENTATION fields

	dxf: don't skip IDBUFFER r13-r14

	dxf: fix UCS
	misspelled the UCSTableRecord

