2020-03-09  Reini Urban  <rurban@cpan.org>

	fix TU32 type for r2007+, either UCS-2 or UCS-4
	I suspect this is either a Teigha or AutoCAD bug.
	But the TU32 feature strings can be either 4 or 2 byte.

