2019-07-15  Reini Urban  <rurban@cpan.org>

	expand [rcount1], [rcount2] to [%d] for LOG_TRACE
	better logging.

	It looks expensive, timings:
	                 without     with
	make check       0m12.034s   0m12.303s
	  (mostly -v2)
	./logs-all.sh    0m35.934s   0m37.324s
	  (only -v4)
	so it's neglectable.
